    <section address="Section1">
      <title>Array Functions</title>
      <content>
        <table>
          <tableHeader>
            <row>
              <entry>
                <para>Assembly</para>
              </entry>
              <entry>
                <para>Function</para>
              </entry>
              <entry>
                <para>Description</para>
              </entry>
            </row>
          </tableHeader>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.AAdd(XSharp.__Array,XSharp.__Usual@)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      向数组末尾添加新元素。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.AClone(XSharp.__Array)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      复制一个多维数组。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.ACloneShallow(XSharp.__Array)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      浅复制一个数组，不包括其子数组。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.ACopy(XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      将元素从一个数组复制到另一个数组。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.ACopy(XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      Copies elements from one array to another array.
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.ADel(XSharp.__Array,System.UInt32)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      删除数组元素。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.ADel(XSharp.__FoxArray,System.Int32,System.Int32)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
            Deletes an element from a one-dimensional array, or a row or column from a two-dimensional array.
        </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.ADim(XSharp.__Array)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>Calculate the # of dimensions in an array</para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.ADimPic(XSharp.__Array)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>Calculate a string that represents the dimensions in an array</para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.ADir(XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      用目录信息填充一系列数组。
      注意：
      ADir() 是一个兼容性函数，因此不推荐使用。
      它被 Directory() 函数取代，后者将所有文件信息返回在一个多维数组中。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.ADir(XSharp.__Array,System.String,System.String,System.Int32)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      Places information about files into an array and then returns the number of files.
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.AElement(XSharp.__FoxArray,System.UInt32)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
            Returns the number of an array element from the element's subscripts.
        </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.AEval(XSharp.__Array,XSharp.ICodeblock)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      对数组中的每个元素执行代码块。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.AEvalA(XSharp.__Array,XSharp.ICodeblock)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      对数组中的每个元素执行代码块，并将返回值赋给数组中的每个元素。
    </para>
