          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.AEvalOld(XSharp.__Array,XSharp.ICodeblock,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      对数组中的每个元素执行代码块。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.AFields(XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      用当前数据库文件的结构填充数组。
      注意：
      AFields() 是一个兼容性函数，因此不推荐使用。
      它已被 DBStruct() 取代，后者不需要在调用前存在任何数组，并返回一个包含当前数据库文件结构的多维数组。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.AFields(XSharp.__Array,XSharp.__Usual)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      Retrieves and stores information about the structure of the table in a specified work area, specified by a table alias, or in the currently selected work area in an array and returns the number of fields in the table.
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.AFill(XSharp.__Array,XSharp.__Usual@,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      用指定值填充数组元素。
    </para>
