          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.AIns(XSharp.__FoxArray,System.UInt32,System.UInt32)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
            Inserts an element into a one-dimensional array, or a row or column into a two-dimensional array.
