            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.ASort(XSharp.__Array,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual,XSharp.__Usual)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      Sorts elements in an array in ascending or descending order.
